James Daly (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Daly_(actor) 0 James Firman Daly (October 23, 1918 – July 3, 1978) was an American theater, film and television actor, who is perhaps best known for his role as Paul Lochner in the hospital drama series Medical Center, in which he played Chad Everett's superior.
